data.description: Bonus Room! Enjoy this super spacious home in Western Plateau! Featuring 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2 car attached garage with Storm Shelter!  Additional bonus room off the master could be used as an office or man cave! Enjoy the open kitchen which offers the perfect space for entertaining! It offers double oven, gas range, plentiful cabinet space, kitchen island and the beautiful bay window in the dining area. The living room has a vaulted ceiling with exposed beams and a centered brick fireplace to bring it all together. The isolated master bedroom has 2 separate closets, as well as a wood burning stove fireplace! The remaining 2 bedrooms have great closet space. Enjoy the awesome backyard which offers a nice patio, fenced dog run and a STORAGE BUILDING with electricity!  Call today
